data.description: Step into 214 Forest Ave - this charming home nestled in the heart of Erlanger. This first thing you notice is the warm hardwood floors that grace the main level's spacious living and dining rooms. The kitchen, accentuated by fresh vinyl flooring & beautiful white cabinets, complements the recently remodeled bathroom upstairs, featuring a modern tub/shower combo. Two good-sized bedrooms await on the upper level, bathed in natural light from the large windows. The basement offers ample storage space, ensuring every item has its place.   Outside, the tiered deck is a haven for relaxation, set against the backdrop of a large, private, fenced yard. Plenty of room to run and play here! Convenience is paramount with a built-in 1-car garage and an extended driveway.  Located on a quaint street, you're moments away from the local elementary school, neighborhood park, and bus line. Discover the blend of comfort and charm at this home has to offer - the perfect start to your homeownership journey.
